title: When a potato salad is served, you know it is Christmas
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary: Canadian Naomi Hužovičová talks about traditional Slovak food on the Christmas Eve table, from different soups to a carp served with potato salad. Enjoy your bite of Slovak Christmas.
